<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - InvestyInYourFuture</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/InvestyInYourFuture.styles.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-light navbar-toggleable-sm  box-shadow mb-3 fixed">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                    <img src="~/images/main-logo-f.png" alt="logo" />
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav flex-grow-1">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Projects</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Creators</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Founders</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">About us</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Contact</a>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="main-container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer-wrapper ">
        <div class="footer-top row container">
            <div class="footer-image-inner col-3">
                <img src="~/images/main-logo-f.png" alt="logo" />
            </div>
            
            <div class="footer-top-inner row col-9">
                <div class="text-group col-6">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce consequat quam et quam scelerisque, a varius dui tincidunt. Curabitur sed gravida mauris. Donec at hendrerit elit. Nullam ut velit tellus. Nullam eu neque bibendum, dapibus est id, dignissim mi.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-menu col-6">
                    <h4>MENU</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-menu-list">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Projects</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Creators</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Founders</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">About us</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="" asp-action="">Contact</a>
                        </li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            &copy; 2023 - InvestyInYourFuture - <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy</a>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/main.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
